Class CustomerReport

java.lang.Object
entities.Report
entities.CustomerReport
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class CustomerReport extends Report implements Serializable
CustomerReport Include data to create Histogram Chart Of Customers The Graph will show 10%,20%.....100% Distbution , Based On Money Customer Spent In Area In specific Month. Also store Biggest Order Count UserName,Most Expense User
